[SPEAKER_00]: I hope so.

52
00:05:11,180 --> 00:05:11,661
[SPEAKER_00]: Thank you.

53
00:05:12,922 --> 00:05:19,406
[SPEAKER_01]: So we know the chamber is celebrating its 100th anniversary this year.

54
00:05:21,622 --> 00:05:25,823
[SPEAKER_01]: You've had, I mean, I know a lot of successful events, Oktoberfest.

55
00:05:26,743 --> 00:05:29,663
[SPEAKER_01]: I mean, there's a lot of events you guys do.

56
00:05:30,724 --> 00:05:32,664
