62
00:05:51,381 --> 00:06:11,290
[SPEAKER_00]: We've been doing a lot more of our speaker series meeting with more of the town, and it's this all leading up to our hundred celebration at the bear hall, and we've sort of thrown out our traditional model of what our annual banquet is with speeches.

63
00:06:12,438 --> 00:06:20,204
[SPEAKER_00]: and awards and we give the citizen of the year and we have scholarships and it's a great event.

64
00:06:20,804 --> 00:06:23,767
[SPEAKER_00]: But this year we've moved our awards to a luncheon.

65
00:06:25,900 --> 00:06:31,623
[SPEAKER_00]: And we're very happy that the luncheon is going to actually be at Bistro 489 at the high school.

66
