[SPEAKER_01]: It really is.

105
00:08:08,063 --> 00:08:14,948
[SPEAKER_01]: So one thing that residents, I mean, I notice it, and I'm sure a lot of people that live in Method notice it.

106
00:08:15,549 --> 00:08:19,451
[SPEAKER_01]: I mean, it seems like every business associated with the chamber

107
00:08:21,125 --> 00:08:22,686
