[SPEAKER_00]: I hope the businesses understand that from us.

115
00:08:39,622 --> 00:08:50,370
[SPEAKER_00]: But your question is really interesting because it seems to be that the businesses who are invested in this community, they're in the chamber.

116
00:08:50,791 --> 00:08:56,375
[SPEAKER_00]: They join the chamber because they're such strong community partners.

117
00:08:58,228 --> 00:09:04,970
