178
00:13:22,716 --> 00:13:23,076
[SPEAKER_00]: Great.

179
00:13:23,276 --> 00:13:26,298
[SPEAKER_00]: Yeah, you know, we are not funded by City Hall.

180
00:13:26,338 --> 00:13:29,259
[SPEAKER_00]: We are a member funded organization.

181
00:13:29,279 --> 00:13:35,721
[SPEAKER_00]: Okay, so, but we do some joint events with the city.

182
00:13:36,381 --> 00:13:41,803
[SPEAKER_00]: And the city gives us a lot of support for Oktoberfest, which we really appreciate.

183
00:13:41,843 --> 00:13:43,544
[SPEAKER_00]: We're allowed to close down the streets.

184
00:13:44,264 --> 00:13:45,925
[SPEAKER_00]: And we make, you know, showcase

185
00:13:46,652 --> 00:13:50,695
[SPEAKER_00]: All the businesses in Medford can participate in Oktoberfest.

186
00:13:51,315 --> 00:14:00,562
[SPEAKER_00]: You know, we do the work to organize that event and we appreciate all their support and making that happen because we couldn't shut down the roads without the city's concern.

187
00:14:00,722 --> 00:14:06,826
