188
00:14:08,882 --> 00:14:14,293
[SPEAKER_00]: But there are times when we have different opinions on how things should go.

189
00:14:14,313 --> 00:14:18,262
[SPEAKER_00]: I also respect that we have, that we're separate.

190
00:14:19,484 --> 00:14:25,686
[SPEAKER_00]: Okay, they are in no way do I report to the city that I report to a board of directors.

191
00:14:26,447 --> 00:14:30,488
